!!!   READ THIS BEFORE USING THE SPYSENDER  !!!
DONT FORGET TO READ THE INCLUDED HELP
Use this program (locater) to control all your spysenders around the world. This
is still a BETA version, so not everything may work as I wanted it to
By the way: when you see an error like WARFTPD ALREADY RUNNING or something like
that just ignore it and press OK. Please note that you should NOT run any FTP-Servers
BEFORE starting the Spysender locater! This is because the spysender sends information
to the FTP-Port and thus that port needs to be free!
The icon you see appearing at the bottom-right of your screen is the FTP-Server. You should
terminate this program AFTER using the locater. This FTP-Server will retrieve all the
information for you, so make sure it is runnning properly! You might also want to check the settings.
If you are not familiar with configuring this FTP-Server, then just DONT TOUCH it! It has been
correctly configured to make the locater and spysender talk. Please note that this FTP-Server gives
access to the spysender to your C DRIVE only! So NEVER try to retrieve an image or a file at your D Drive.
(if you do wish this to enable this, examine the FTP-Server a little bit)
Do not use the AUTO-Update function yet! Please examine our website (www.spysend.com) first for additional
files and help. If you have ANY questions, just mail them to spysender@spysend.com or contact me at ICQ. My
Next to that I would like to ask you NOT to abuse this software ;-) .... HAVE FUN!
